The '''Shop''' is a [[Main Menu]] page where users can purchase content from VRChat, or from the community. Content can be purchased with [[VRChat Credits]], and the types of content ranges from avatars, [[Creator Economy#Listings|listings]] from world & group [[Creator Economy#Stores|stores]], and listings which include content types from the [[Inventory]].

==Types of content==
Content that can appear in the store include:
* Inventory content
** [[Emojis|Emoji]]
** [[Stickers]]
** [[Items]]
** [[Inventory#Cosmetics|Cosmetics]]
*** [[Camera Drone|Drones]]
*** [[Portals]]
*** [[Loading Screens]]
*** [[Warp Effects]]
* [[Accessories]]
* Avatars from the [[Avatar Marketplace]]
* World stores
* Group stores

== Layout ==
The Shop is split up into 5 sections: Exclusive, Avatars, Accessories, World Stores, Group Stores. Listings for portals, items, and other content types include 3D previews.

=== Exclusive ===
Exclusive or the VRChat Store is where VRChat sells content from themselves, which are limited to Inventory content types. They are offered as listings, each listing has products which include are the type of content the user will receive. Listings can be free, or purchased with VRChat Credits, and could be available for a limited amount of time.

====VRC+ discounts====
Listings offered in the shop are discounted if a user is subscribed to [[VRC+]]. These are indicated with a "{{Credits|}} with VRC+" line underneath the original price.

====Shelves====
Shelves are how the store is organized, each shelf is curated to a specific focus, such as a set of listings for an event or an update. 

