=== Avatars ===
The Avatars section is the home of the [[Avatar Marketplace]]. 

====Categories====
The avatars are organized by category. Categories show the first 4 avatars, with the option to view all avatars within the category. The categories and the avatars within the categories are dynamic, meaning it may be moved, removed or populated/refreshed with new avatars without notice.

The categories include:

* Popular (Weekly)
* New
* Under 1200 Credits
* Anime
* Furry
* Human
* Marketplace A-Z
* Sci-Fi
* Cartoon
* [[Public Avatars|Public]]
* Animal
* Fantasy 
* Realistic
* Objects
* Pop Culture
* Fashion

====Filters & sorts====
Avatars can be filtered and sorted to narrow the results of the avatar users would like to find. They can be filtered or sorted by the clicking either the "filter" icon or the "Sorted by" button. After applying a filter or sort, it will open a new page with the filtered & sorted results. 

The filter and sort options include:

'''Filters''':
* Search
* Tags
** Sci-Fi, Animal, Cartoon, Anime, Furry, Realistic, Fantasy, Human, Objects, Fashion, Pop Culture
* Availability
** Marketplace, Public
* Platform
** This Platform, PC, Android
* Performance
** Excellent, Good and up, Medium and up, Poor and up, All

'''Sorts''': 
* Default
* Date Added
* Last Updated
* Name
* Performance

