=== World & Group stores ===
The World & Group store pages showcase a curated set of worlds or groups that have [[Creator Economy#Stores|stores]]. When within a world that has a store, clicking "World Stores" will bring up the store for that world. 

==Gifting==
When selecting a listing, users are able to gift it instead of buying it for themselves, by clicking the gift button next to the purchase button. When gifting, users will be able to choose to gift to a user within the instance or from their friends list. Users may only gift listings from the Shop if they reach the [[Trust Rank]] "User".

